  suffices AEMeasurable ((rangeSplitting g ∘ rangeFactorization g) ∘ f) μ by
    rwa [(rightInverse_rangeSplitting hg.injective).comp_eq_id] at this
  exact hg.measurable_rangeSplitting.comp_aemeasurable H.subtype_mk
